parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The erratic steering issue can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle pulls to the left or right
the steering wheel shakes or vibrates
the vehicle does not hold center
the steering feels stiff or loose
and the vehicle pulls to one side when starting the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The power steering failure can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The power steering becomes difficult to maneuver
the steering wheel is hard to turn
and the vehicle pulls to one side.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The battery-related steering issues can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The steering issues are resolved after replacing the battery
the vehicle pulls to one side
and the steering feels stiff or loose.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the occupants of the vehicle may not receive the necessary protection to prevent harm.
symptoms: Airbags did not deploy in a crash
despite the severity of the impact
resulting in injuries or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Airbag malfunctions can lead to injuries or fatalities, as the airbags may not deploy properly or may deploy unexpectedly, causing harm to the occupants of the vehicle.
symptoms: Airbags deployed unexpectedly
did not deploy at all
or deployed improperly
resulting in injuries or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The Takata airbag recall issues can lead to injuries or fatalities, as the airbags may not deploy properly or may deploy explosively, causing harm to the occupants of the vehicle.
symptoms: Airbags did not deploy or deployed improperly
resulting in injuries or fatalities
and issues with the recall process
including incomplete or inaccurate information.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle may move unexpectedly, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or property damage.
symptoms: The vehicle rolls down an inclined driveway
fails to respond to the brake pedal
or moves forward while the foot is on the brake.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and loud explosion of the sunroof can cause driver distraction, loss of control, and potential accidents.
symptoms: A loud
frightening explosion sound from the sunroof area
often accompanied by shattered glass and debris.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Torque converter issues can cause unexpected acceleration, loss of power, or stalling, which can lead to accidents or strand the driver.
symptoms: Unusual noises
vibrations
or hesitation when accelerating
often accompanied by a check engine light.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake system failures can cause accidents, injuries, or property damage due to the inability to stop the vehicle.
symptoms: Sudden
unexpected activation of the brake system
or a failure to respond to the brake pedal.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Door lock and hinge problems can cause accidents, injuries, or property damage due to unexpected door openings or closures.
symptoms: Doors that lock or unlock unexpectedly
or hinges that fail to hold the door in place
leading to accidents or damage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical and infotainment system failures can cause distractions, accidents, or inconvenience to the driver.
symptoms: Unusual noises
malfunctions
or failures of the infotainment system
backup camera
or blind spot monitoring system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Air conditioning and mold issues can cause health problems, discomfort, or unpleasant odors for the driver and passengers.
symptoms: Unusual odors
mold growth
or malfunctions of the air conditioning system.
